reviewText: Rotten tomato these, but this 2 pack was a great deal and the quality is just fine on my 1080p 7th gen samsung.

This was a super price for these two movies. Idiocracy is really underrated. It is almost prophetic on how our society is headed. And Airheads goes well with Idoicracy.  Buying these you can't go wrong if you have a sense of humor.
